# =============================================================================
# Sentinel ZTNA — application artifacts
# =============================================================================

# ML pipeline outputs — model.joblib/metrics.json are committed on purpose
# so Docker builds don't have to retrain (heavy: 5-fold CV + search + MLP)
# on the deploy host. Regenerate both via `make train` after model changes.
backend/app/ml/artifacts/dataset.csv
backend/app/ml/artifacts/*.png

# Runtime logs
*.log
logs/

